Sales Dashboard Requirements

------------------------------------------------------------
Dashboard Purpose
------------------------------------------------------------
- Present overview of sales metrics and trends
- Support performance analysis
- Help identify sales patterns

------------------------------------------------------------
KPI Overview
------------------------------------------------------------
- Show total sales (current year and previous year)
- Show total profits (current year and previous year)
- Show total quantity sold (current year and previous year)

------------------------------------------------------------
Sales Trends
------------------------------------------------------------
- Monthly data for sales, profit, and quantity
- Include current year and previous year
- Highlight month with highest sales
- Highlight month with lowest sales

------------------------------------------------------------
Product Subcategory Comparison
------------------------------------------------------------
- Compare sales by product subcategory
- Include current year and previous year

------------------------------------------------------------
Weekly Trends for Sales & Profit
------------------------------------------------------------
- Weekly sales data (current year)
- Weekly profit data (current year)
- Show average weekly sales
- Show average weekly profit
- Highlight weeks above average
- Highlight weeks below average

------------------------------------------------------------
Customer Distribution by Number of Orders
------------------------------------------------------------
- Show distribution of customers by number of orders
- Identify customer behavior patterns

------------------------------------------------------------
Top Customers by Profit
------------------------------------------------------------
- List top 10 customers by profit
- Include rank
- Include number of orders
- Include current sales
- Include current profit
- Include last order date

------------------------------------------------------------
Dashboard Dynamics
------------------------------------------------------------
- Allow year selection for historical data
- Enable navigation between dashboards
- Make charts interactive for filtering

------------------------------------------------------------
Data Filters
------------------------------------------------------------
- Filter by product category
- Filter by product subcategory
- Filter by region
- Filter by state
- Filter by city

------------------------------------------------------------
Suggested Visuals
------------------------------------------------------------
- Sparkline for compact trends
- Line chart for monthly and weekly comparisons

------------------------------------------------------------
Sample Metrics
------------------------------------------------------------
- Previous year sales: $829K
- Current year sales: $1.2M
